summary: Do you have any limitations on what kind of quotes can be submitted? Like say... raunchy subject matter or course language or...
question: Do you have any limitations on what kind of quotes can be submitted? Like say... raunchy subject matter or course language or the like?
answer:
Raunchy subject matter and course language are allowed, but there are some words that we really want to avoid, such as the N-word, the R-word (and variations thereof), and the C-word to name a few. 

General rule of thumb is “if you can’t say it in the workplace without losing your job, please try not to say it here”. 

We do have a rules page right here that we’ll update with clearer rules soon as well. And the mods have the ability to accept or decline any submissions we get, so if you are worried something you submitted might be over the line, or are unsure, you can ask us to review it. If we accidentally post something offensive, whether it’s our own posts or submissions, please let us know and we’ll delete it immediately. Our top priority is the happiness and safety of all our followers.

We’ll post about any and all updates to the rules and changes in management in the future. We want to keep all of you in the loop on matters like this and we accept constructive criticism on how to make the blog more fun and inclusive. 

I hope this helps!

-Mod Retsuko

title: Aggretsroleplay! The 18+ Aggretsuko roleplay server!
body:
HEY YOU! Wanna roleplay as your favorite character from Aggretsuko with a bunch of other people roleplaying their favorite characters?!

Well look no further! A brand new 18+ server has been created for just such a purpose! We are allowing both canon characters and original characters, and as of now, it is completely empty! So join up and snag yourself your favorite character before someone else does!

If you’re interested in joining, please send a message to my account here on tumblr, SatiricalGaming. Remember that this is an 18+ server, so if you are below that age, you will not be able to join. Just let me know what character you want to be and I’ll send you the link to the discord and place your name by that character!

This roleplay is strictly for those who are fluent in English!

Our list of available characters is as follows:

summary: Okay, so I finished Aggretsuko s2 a few days ago and can I just say that I cannot emphasize enough how much I love the fact that...
body:
Okay, so I finished Aggretsuko s2 a few days ago and can I just say that I cannot emphasize enough how much I love the fact that Retsuko always has to end relationships because they’re not right for HER, not because they’re inherently abusive or “toxic” or whatever.

It’s just … I don’t see stories tackle these types of relationship dilemmas enough. Finally, a show that’s like, “Sometimes thinks won’t work out because you two aren’t right for each other and not because anyone’s evil or something” and I think that’s so much more common in real life and not nearly explored enough. It’s so refreshing. Like, you don’t need to wait for a REASON to be discontented with your relationship if it’s not working NOW and -

I just fucking love Aggretsuko.
